{"tid":338809,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"向教會歌說不！  淺談填詞的0243 (下)","createTime":"2017-07-28T13:10:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T16:42:48.000Z","uid":45011,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6b801549316b79e22fe92e6a5d7b0c32d7523d85","tid":338809,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:10:05.000Z","msg":"想有更佳閱讀效果，可以係小弟個Blog Page睇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://aamusictravel.com/2017/07/28/%E5%A1%AB%E8%A9%9E%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7-%E6%B7%BA%E8%AB%870243-%E4%B8%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.com%2F2017%2F07%2F28%2F%25E5%25A1%25AB%25E8%25A9%259E%25E6%258A%2580%25E5%25B7%25A7-%25E6%25B7%25BA%25E8%25AB%25870243-%25E4%25B8%258B%2F&d=leWPXQtwudMQbat4Q4cCN6S6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=8b271e22\" target=\"_blank\">https://aamusictravel.com/2017/07/28/%E5%A1%AB%E8%A9%9E%E6%8A%80%E5%B7%A7-%E6%B7%BA%E8%AB%870243-%E4%B8%8B/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上回講到0243的基本應用，留下《K歌之王》和《囍帖街》兩道題目，不知大家做好功課沒有?<br />\n<br />\n《淺談0243(上)》傳送門: <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/322951/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/322951/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n《K歌之王》 陳奕迅<br />\n<br />\nVerse 1<br />\n243 3420 4240<br />\n42404 4243<br />\n<br />\n243 3420 4243<br />\n34204 3340 2434<br />\n<br />\nPre-chorus 1<br />\n00023 34242434<br />\n00243 3203343<br />\n<br />\n00023 42434420<br />\n24330 42434<br />\n<br />\nChorus 1<br />\n00234 324343342<br />\n02434 43342002434<br />\n00234 20023~330<br />\n02434 43942 4444434<br />\n<br />\n342434 333420<br />\n0024 033304 3330 24<br />\n<br />\nVerse 2<br />\n243 3420 4240<br />\n42404 4243<br />\n<br />\n243 3420 4243<br />\n34204 33433 2434<br />\n<br />\nChorus 2<br />\n00234 324343342<br />\n02434 43342002434<br />\n00234 20023~330<br />\n02434 43942 4444434<br />\n<br />\nBridge:<br />\n342242243334 02444343<br />\n342242233334 43333420<br />\n0024 033304 3330 24<br />\n<br />\nVerse 3:<br />\n243 3420 4240<br />\n0443423302 02024<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對，我想就算你本來就對音準很拿手，不會錯，你的答案可能仍然跟我的不一樣。喔？那是你錯還是我錯，還是大家都錯？不！大家都對！<br />\n再看看《囍帖街》有否這個情況？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《囍帖街》 謝安琪<br />\n<br />\nVerse 1A:<br />\n024433 03334 44430<br />\n244 03333 442433<br />\n333 03342 34230<br />\n0224333442 44433<br />\n<br />\nVerse 1B:<br />\n24433 03334 44430<br />\n244 03333 442433<br />\n33344202 33333420<br />\n430 2433343 2433424<br />\n<br />\nChorus 1:<br />\n024433 333333442433<br />\n3333442023442200 020242<br />\n<br />\n024433 333344224200<br />\n333333443 34004<br />\n33423024<br />\n<br />\nVerse 2:<br />\n024433 03334 44430<br />\n244 03333 4422434<br />\n33344202 33333420<br />\n430 2433343 2433424<br />\n<br />\nChorus 2:<br />\n024433 333333442433<br />\n3333442023442200 020242<br />\n<br />\n024433 333344224200<br />\n333333443 34004<br />\n33400424<br />\n32434430 34<br />\n<br />\n我想這個問題都逃不掉的。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>聲調偏移</ins></strong><br />\n看看《囍帖街》的副歌：<br />\n<br />\n忘掉愛過的他<br />\n當初的喜帖金箔印着那位他<br />\n裱起婚紗照那道牆及一切美「麗舊年華」<br />\n明日同步拆下<br />\n<br />\n相信最大問題的就是出現在這裡，也是我們詞人常常觀察到的現象(並非問題，對我們而言是好事，因為聲調選取多一個選擇，選詞用字的範圍就大一倍)。黃偉文填詞的時候，和我的答案都是選取了「2200」填進去的，然而你可能填了「3333」，或者可以把這句歌詞改成<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裱起婚紗照那道牆但一切都「相當虛假」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不理會詞義，只看音準這一因素，你會發現這樣填同樣合音，「相當虛假」正是「3333」調的字，同樣道理，你這回用「3344」、其實一樣不違和:<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n裱起婚紗照那道牆及一切都「粉飾美化」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那麼這些配搭又是否「百搭」呢？當然不是，上面用過「2200」、「3333」和「3344」，卻不可以「2244」或者「3300」，這是因為我們將整個斷句的聲調都偏移了，2轉0降一度，所以可以選擇的就只可以降一度，3轉4降一度，2轉4升一度，3轉0降三度，所以可以看得出分別，那麼3轉3明明就是沒有分別，為何又可以呢? 其實我是在用「3399」的概念，但加上9這個調會亂上好幾倍，而且有不少的9調既可向3走又可向4走，會把問題更複雜化，暫且不贅。最重要的，是你能找到一個合音的答案，你不需要知道清楚哪些字有其他聲調選擇，儲夠了經驗，你不刻意去想這個問題，也會很快知道答案的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n==========================================================<br />\n<br />\n小弟其他音樂作品及文章:<br />\n<a href=\"https://aamusictravel.com/category/music-%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamusictravel.com%2Fcategory%2Fmusic-%25E9%259F%25B3%25E6%25A8%2582%2F&d=leWPXQtwudMQbat4Q4cCN6S6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=9cbff5e1\" target=\"_blank\">https://aamusictravel.com/category/music-%E9%9F%B3%E6%A8%82/</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook專頁: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/aamusictravel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Faamusictravel%2F&d=leWPXQtwudMQbat4Q4cCN6S6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=a49ee447\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/aamusictravel/</a>"},{"pid":"3b4dcac490f446705ff4621f8f63bae295155125","tid":338809,"uid":40429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:15:26.000Z","msg":"終於有下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350f1efeab3a23033d4f74d730223033deee2fb0","tid":338809,"uid":45011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T13:18:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>終於有下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實寫上既時候已經寫埋，不過我Schedule左2星期後先出，講真都係得今日先得閒Post上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7e01a51dc32461b480a23b8dab0dace0612c2fa","tid":338809,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"下回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87a3d1e1dc4662d4fd129d919c730b51c5fdc6d0","tid":338809,"uid":55420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T17:31:20.000Z","msg":"以前有試過用數字配落歌詞，但冇諗過原來淨係0243都已經夠用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac7807ea762bf0988703a3f33d28f16152224899","tid":338809,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T17:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前有試過用數字配落歌詞，但冇諗過原來淨係0243都已經夠用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想再分得仔細啲可以加埋9同5入去，但一般嚟講0243已經夠做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6